<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - MyWeb</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .platform-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px 20px;
    }
    .platform-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f093fb, #f5576c, #ffd700);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .platform-header p { color: #8888aa; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .games-grid {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .game-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      display: block;
    }
    .game-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }
    .card-icon {
      height: 160px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 4rem;
    }
    .card-body { padding: 16px 20px 20px; }
    .card-body h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .card-body p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #8888aa; line-height: 1.5; }
    .card-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #666;
    }
    .high-score { color: #ffd700; font-weight: 600; }
    .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .tag-puzzle { background: rgba(99,179,237,0.2); color: #63b3ed; }
    .tag-strategy { background: rgba(72,187,120,0.2); color: #48bb78; }
    .tag-casual { background: rgba(237,137,54,0.2); color: #ed8936; }
    .tag-action { background: rgba(245,101,101,0.2); color: #f56565; }
    .bg-goose { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d1b69, #11998e); }
    .bg-chess { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #e94560); }
    .bg-hide { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3443, #34e89e); }
    .bg-diff { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50, #3498db); }
    .bg-match { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ee9ca7, #ffdde1); }
    .bg-fps { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #e74c3c); }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 30px; color: #555; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .platform-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .games-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="platform-header">
    <h1>🎮 MyWeb 游戏平台</h1>
    <p>精选休闲小游戏，随时随地畅玩</p>
  </header>
  <div class="games-grid">
    <a class="game-card" href="/games/goose-game/index.html">
      <div class="card-icon bg-goose">🦆</div>
      <div class="card-body"><h3>抓大鹅</h3><p>经典三消堆叠玩法，三层方块等你来挑战！</p></div>
      <div class="card-footer"><span class="tag tag-puzzle">益智</span><span class="high-score" data-game="goose_game">最高分: --</span></div>
    </a>
    <a class="game-card" href="/games/chess/index.html">
      <div class="card-icon bg-chess">♟️</div>
      <div class="card-body"><h3>中国象棋</h3><p>楚河汉界，双人对战，体验千年棋艺</p></div>
      <div class="card-footer"><span class="tag tag-strategy">策略</span><span class="high-score" data-game="chinese_chess">胜局: --</span></div>
    </a>
    <a class="game-card" href="/games/hide-seek/index.html">
      <div class="card-icon bg-hide">🔍</div>
      <div class="card-body"><h3>捉迷藏</h3><p>隐藏物件寻找，考验你的观察力！</p></div>
      <div class="card-footer"><span class="tag tag-casual">休闲</span><span class="high-score" data-game="hide_seek">最高分: --</span></div>
    </a>
    <a class="game-card" href="/games/spot-diff/index.html">
      <div class="card-icon bg-diff">🧐</div>
      <div class="card-body"><h3>找不同</h3><p>双图找茬，火眼金睛谁最强？</p></div>
      <div class="card-footer"><span class="tag tag-casual">休闲</span><span class="high-score" data-game="spot_diff">最高分: --</span></div>
    </a>
    <a class="game-card" href="/games/match-game/index.html">
      <div class="card-icon bg-match">🍬</div>
      <div class="card-body"><h3>开心消消乐</h3><p>经典三消益智，连锁消除超过瘾！</p></div>
      <div class="card-footer"><span class="tag tag-puzzle">益智</span><span class="high-score" data-game="match_game">最高分: --</span></div>
    </a>
    <a class="game-card" href="/games/fps-game/index.html">
      <div class="card-icon bg-fps">🔫</div>
      <div class="card-body"><h3>FPS 射击</h3><p>第一人称射击，靶场训练+敌人AI+多武器系统</p></div>
      <div class="card-footer"><span class="tag tag-action">动作</span><span class="high-score" data-game="fps_game">最高分: --</span></div>
    </a>
    <a class="game-card" href="/games/adventure/index.html">
      <div class="card-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f3443,#34e89e,#0d1b2a)">🏔️</div>
      <div class="card-body"><h3>幻境探索</h3><p>3D开放世界冒险，收集宝石，消灭怪物！</p></div>
      <div class="card-footer"><span class="tag tag-action">冒险</span><span class="high-score" data-game="adventure">最高分: --</span></div>
    </a>
  </div>
  <footer><p>&copy; 2026 MyWeb 游戏平台</p></footer>
  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.high-score').forEach(el => {
      const score = localStorage.getItem('highscore_' + el.dataset.game);
      if (score) el.textContent = el.textContent.replace('--', score);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
